{"tid":493003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"夜總會女公關疑遭人掟落樓死亡　重案拘男友助查　（耀揚...）","createTime":"2017-12-08T05:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T17:42:10.000Z","uid":141060,"like":133,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"1eef7049ababa56396445870a25d2fd931857a73","tid":493003,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:48:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/bkn-20171208110442143-1208_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171208%2Fbkn-20171208110442143-1208_00822_001.html&d=UYGkvbzWySGVpgnXueqqfDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=63c8a8e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171208/bkn-20171208110442143-1208_00822_001.html</a><br />\n夜總會女公關疑遭人掟落樓死亡　重案拘男友助查<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/134814_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F134814_156005c5baf40ff51a327f1c34f2975b.jpg&h=5af6bbf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【13:15】女死者姓黃，33歲，在夜總會任女關，同居男友姓劉，在律師行任文員，事發前兩人發生激烈衝突，女死者遭人用硬物扑傷頭部。警員到場時，單位一名男子企圖離開，遭警員截停調查。<br />\n<br />\n【13:00】現場消息稱，事發時，單位內曾傳出男女吵架聲。<br />\n<br />\n【12:20】10多名探員抵達河泉樓，調查女子墮樓事件有否可疑，案件交重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n沙田女子墮樓亡，早上10時39分，一名30餘歲女子，被發現由水泉澳邨河泉樓高處墮下，倒臥平台上重傷，消防員接報到場將其救下，由救護車送往醫院後證實身亡。警方事後調派多輛警車到場，正對事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/08/134824_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F08%2F134824_f3ccdd27d2000e3f9255a7e3e2c48800.jpg&h=012ed4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa4ab77666bba6ec355b4b9af1a31b55e5958c6","tid":493003,"uid":99856,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:49:18.000Z","msg":"水泉澳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92cfcf31ac91ea475947dc7dcd36f6cb3de9608d","tid":493003,"uid":146243,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:54:14.000Z","msg":"屌水泉奧呢條垃圾邨 成條劃做集中營啦"},{"pid":"d72738590faa454c8c6b9e4242d9d29b543f60fe","tid":493003,"uid":85819,"like":67,"dislike":2,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T05:54:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebb2e37dec9110bbb4430ccabbd6621a61cab38c","tid":493003,"uid":39539,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6007cbfcb16a56395c9764871a2f827526c533d","tid":493003,"uid":74442,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"交返畀公安做啦"},{"pid":"f31e16a37e12340871ccc2ba0777304ec62a8383","tid":493003,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲之村！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc403c12b208cf626948a646fa6a5b2f7ac9271","tid":493003,"uid":49588,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"應該改下：<br />\n來自中國大陸地獄鬼國嘅女公關⋯"},{"pid":"4c7b3779393a6f8d421ab59b5ebe74f0ec84c517","tid":493003,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:06:29.000Z","msg":"烏鴉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c500f5dd503e849009e278d3d4cd7e48e56d81","tid":493003,"uid":33338,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:06:59.000Z","msg":"你未試過咩？ 真係好好fee