ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"係咪佳佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9599297093e9d4eb366f2d074d20d27198ae7765","tid":493003,"uid":4173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:43:54.000Z","msg":"你唔做雞我邊有錢養你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe818a9cd2219b5f68a6bab3541f4d5df35cf480","tid":493003,"uid":154963,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T06:54:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實就咁睇條屍分唔分得出係 掟落樓定跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跳樓腳直插落地  俾人掟會頭落/水平落？</blockquote><br />\n下 但咁高層跳落黎仲可以直插落地 跳水都未必得啦"},{"pid":"804d43da0b8988d7d23307ba0566c16143750c38","tid":493003,"uid":13421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:03:59.000Z","msg":"睇錯重案狗男友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048313ccf6a6dd4401aed4f44c6ea16baeeebc09","tid":493003,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:04:56.000Z","msg":"又係水泉澳<br />\n今朝先有個初生B猝死"},{"pid":"817cf4526c25b1d4964a080890f033da8cffd84b","tid":493003,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>烏鴉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係耀揚"},{"pid":"220b5bdcc5d21273d589d4336569f9696b4110c4","tid":493003,"uid":69071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:07:29.000Z","msg":"人以群分 物以類聚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3616964eca25af231481124543126dd7bdef9c","tid":493003,"uid":152420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"暈咗點跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6843b4c0e8600cb929