r />\n班四川湖南支那賤畜，講鄉下話<br />\n<br />\n有文化有公的支那人都未必黎"},{"pid":"615d348afe8db73d64042b6c5c0a4935e69c3252","tid":493003,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"9132ee2647d8c6d2cbc5a2da203f58e03558b760","tid":493003,"uid":50595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:36:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水泉澳好快取代啟晴邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安達都未出聲"},{"pid":"70487bb23b834bb0afb00135f8b4c3ae48b3d756","tid":493003,"uid":39539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:38:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>水泉澳好快取代啟晴邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安達都未出聲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n安達好似仲發展緊，住戶未住滿，將來可能成為全九龍第一大蝗蟲邨"},{"pid":"039e80b3eb2f7dcd96e7c3d609130a58c1ed9863","tid":493003,"uid":37153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實就咁睇條屍分唔分得出係 掟落樓定跳樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知</blockquote><br />\n睇得出 跌落路軌都分到失足定比人推"},{"pid":"c3d22b390b74c8139cadc7b43d0c6781739abd1b","tid":493003,"uid":38820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"#佳佳RIP"},{"pid":"396dfd80c170aa962ee016663666892458969e29","tid":493003,"uid":66825,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"應該將班大陸人集中曬一區，然後離開去其他香港地區要禁區紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf081d3ba0f8784bff365ac391e2660a5b77402d","tid":493003,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水泉澳邨  啟晴村 清河村<br />\n<br />\n邊條先係最多大陸人?<br />\n<br />\n3大 大陸屋村<br />\n<br />\n想搵個識講廣東話既人都唔易</blockquote><br />\n依三個邨已經係支那嘅外飛地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkg